課程概述 Course Description
       透過課堂上實際的教學演示、安排至中學實際面對學生之教學，並將演示情況予以錄影，以及演示後的優缺點之討論，教導有志成為中學英文科教師的師資生，熟悉日後教學之方法與技巧。 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    To familiar students with the contents and steps of major language teachierng methods.    

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Chapter 1 Introduction 2Chapter 2 The Grammar-Translation Method3Chapter 3 The Direct Method4Chapter 4 The Audio-Lingual Method5Chapter 5 Silent way6Chapter 6 Desuggestopedia7Chapter 7 Community Language Learning8Micro-teaching 1,2,3,49Chapter 8 Total Physical Response10Chapter 9 Community Language Teaching11Chapter 10 Content-based12Chapter 11 Task-based13Micro-teaching 5,6,7,814Chapter 12 Participatory Approaches15Chapter 13 Learning Strategy Training
Week 16 (12/31): Cooperative Learning, and MI 
16Chapter 14 Techonology17Micro-teaching 9,10,11,1218Final exam 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


